sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Orch as Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Chunker as Caikit Chunkers<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Services<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS / Caikit NLP<br/>8033|8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI / vLLM<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OTLP as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 1: Classification with Text Generation (v1 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text segments
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (parallel)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    alt Input HAP/PII detected
        Orch-->>Client: 200 OK with detection warnings
    end
    Orch->>TGIS: Generate RPC<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (parallel, output)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>Client: JSON response with generation + detections
    Orch->>OTLP: Export traces + metrics

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 2: OpenAI Chat Completions with Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Optional TLS, Header passthrough
    Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat (input detection on last message)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
    Detector-->>Orch: Input detection results
    alt Streaming mode
        Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (stream=true)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
        loop SSE chunks
            OpenAI-->>Orch: SSE chunk (accumulated in CompletionState)
            Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC bidirectional stream
            Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked output
            Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (batched, parallel)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
            Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
            Orch-->>Client: SSE chunk with detection annotations
        end
    else Unary mode
        Orch->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
        OpenAI-->>Orch: Complete response
        Orch->>Chunker: ChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC, Optional TLS
        Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked output
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (parallel per detector)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
        Detector-->>Orch: Output detection results
        Orch-->>Client: JSON response with detections
    end
    Orch->>OTLP: Export traces + metrics

    Note over Client,OTLP: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>ND-JSON stream, Optional TLS
    loop ND-JSON input chunks
        Orch->>Chunker: BidiStreamingChunkerTokenizationTaskPredict<br/>gRPC bidirectional streaming
        Chunker-->>Orch: Sentence-level chunks
        Orch->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (concurrent, batched)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Optional Bearer
        Detector-->>Orch: Detection results per chunk
        Orch-->>Client: ND-JSON stream with detection results
    end
    Orch->>OTLP: Export traces + metrics
